# Financial Risk Market Incremental Default Risk Charge Amount

## identifier
de8105

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, calculated as at the relevant date, of the regulatory capital default risk on trading book positions that is incremental to the risk captured by the Value at Risk (VaR) based calculation of the reporting party. This item is to be reported where the VaR measures include an estimation of the specific risk charge, and is to be determined in accordance with relevant prudential standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=FinancialRisk.Market.IncrementalDefaultRiskCharge.Amount
- classification=baf/bafot/bafot.02.06
- period=instant
